<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="611" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="14.[1363,2572,1313,2094]" pageId="14" pageNumber="611">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1367,1717,1942,1976]" pageId="14" pageNumber="611">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List as a distinct species. Conservation threats to the North Western Rift Brush-furred Rat are unknown, but its mountain forest habitats have been degraded.
</paragraph>
